dding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\">BBR 借力于区块链技术， 让普通投资者可以参与工业大麻等相关高级药用植物的种植和商用财 富分享中去，享受由特殊高附加值行业带来的巨额收益。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(9, 49, 102); box-sizing: border-box;\">·开心红小豆</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(9, 49, 102); box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" data-ratio=\"1.7772511848341233\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/WUGUT72fomCicIibonenYE84d1Yob3nwotElia7iaibWscaTustxjSM8MZtjtDJvJyjFUkVboWzD0pttKb3BpH6QGog/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"844\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\">开心红小豆是一款区块链游戏，具有更先进的区块链3.0特征，更安全、速度快，扩展性强。它的设计原型类似于之前的网络偷菜游戏，但是它将积分转化为了区块链代币价值，形成社会财富，又进一步突出了社交互动功能。用户不仅可享受种植类游戏的互动乐趣，又可以将成果转化为现实价值，这是一个具备众多优势的创新理念平台。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 50px; display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-style: none none dashed; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/>03-解决商业痛点</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hira