sp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 开心红小豆<br/></span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2020/01/5e22d32342f3d.png\" title=\"e1d47c418ded757a3045e8c1a0ccefe.png\" alt=\"e1d47c418ded757a3045e8c1a0ccefe.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">开心红小豆是一款区块链游戏，具有更先进的区块链3.0特征，更安全、速度快，扩展性强。它的设计原型类似于之前的网络偷菜游戏，但是它将积分转化为了区块链代币价值，形成社会财富，又进一步突出了社交互动功能。用户不仅可享受种植类游戏的互动乐趣，又可以将成果转化为现实价值，这是一个具备众多优势的创新理念平台。</span><br/><br/></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 50px; display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px -55px; padding: 0px; transform: translate3d(-50px, 0px, 0px); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 11px; display: inline-block; width: 70px; height: 80px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/WUGUT72fomDBhwJ8XTxsf4Wlf0ytmSUnN5ibrczkLJuoomODic3auM9RwT7AlsOktRjBouk0nJC71t5ics4joqu7g/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">03<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-style: none none dashed; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">解决商业痛点</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(9, 49, 102); box-sizing: border-box;\">目前的商业痛点：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(9, 49, 102); box-sizing: border-box;\"></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(9, 49, 102); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">一、是中心化的网络结构下，难以保障个人信息的安全。个人信息散落在商业流通的各个环节。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">二、是数据共享。各大企业和机构出于利益考量，以及保护用户隐私的考虑，并不乐意分享用户数据。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">三、是信用系统重复建设，各个系统各自为政。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">四、是欧盟 GDPR 隐私保护给区块链系统带来挑战。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">五、是通过商业行为数据来更好的保护知识产权的利益，让价值获取的过程也融入综合信用体系，提升全面的评判标准。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding